        "2946": {
          "vnum": 2946,
          "name": "Barnacle Patch",
          "description": "You have come to a tunnel whose walls, ceiling and floor are encrusted with barnacles. The bodies of the disgusting little creatures pulsate with the rhythmic tempo of their breathing. The tunnel continues to the east and west. Another chamber is to the north.",
          "grid_x": -1,
          "grid_y": 2,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
              "to_vnum": 2947,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "Mired in Seaweed",
              "direction": "w",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2947": {
          "vnum": 2947,
          "name": "Mired in Seaweed",
          "description": "The walls here glow with a pale green light. The light is evidently sufficient to nurture plant life for this area is practically choked by thick, ropy strands of seaweed. It is only with considerable effort that you force your way through.",
          "grid_x": -2,
          "grid_y": 2,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 2948,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "Eel`s Nest",
              "direction": "n",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2948": {
          "vnum": 2948,
          "name": "Eel`s Nest",
          "description": "The floor of the tunnel is flat and sandy. The water feels somehow charged with excitement and your skin tingles slightly.",
          "grid_x": -2,
          "grid_y": 1,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
              "to_vnum": 2949,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "Sandy Passage",
              "direction": "w",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2949": {
          "vnum": 2949,
          "name": "Sandy Passage",
          "description": "The sandy floor of this broad tunnel heads away from you to the north and south, losing itself in the gloom. There is an opening in the rock wall to your east.",
          "grid_x": -3,
          "grid_y": 1,
          "exits": {
            "s": {
              "to_vnum": 2950,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "Murky Bend",
              "direction": "s",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2950": {
          "vnum": 2950,
          "name": "Murky Bend",
          "description": "The floor is thick with fine silt which turns the water opaque as you pass through. There seems to be a faint glow, a lesser darkness, to the west. A dark space yawns to the north.",
          "grid_x": -3,
          "grid_y": 2,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
              "to_vnum": 2951,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "Coral Garden",
              "direction": "w",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2951": {
          "vnum": 2951,
          "name": "Coral Garden",
          "description": "A diffuse, pearly radiance filters from above to bathe the area in soft green light. Delicate looking growths of coral bask in the light and seem to add their own essence to it. This is a local phenomenon though and you can see dark spaces yawning to the south, east and west. A patch of vibrant green watercress grows here, its leaves crisp and fresh.",
          "grid_x": -4,
          "grid_y": 2,
          "exits": {
            "s": {
              "to_vnum": 2952,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "Dancing Waters",
              "direction": "s",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2952": {
          "vnum": 2952,
          "name": "Dancing Waters",
          "description": "The water here is a pure, crystal blue; the essence of water. On every side, small whirlpools twist and caper with joyous abandon, orbiting you as if to draw you into their merry revelry. The area is suffused with an undertone of fearsome, but benevolent, power. A pale metallic shimmer catches the light.",
          "grid_x": -4,
          "grid_y": 3,
          "exits": {
            "u": {
              "to_vnum": 2953,
              "to_zone": "Undersea Caves",
              "to_room_name": "The Pool",
              "direction": "u",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": true
            }
          },
          "npcs": [
            {
              "name": "Water elemental",
              "description": "So this is the creature - or one like it - that has been gently ushering you forward in the otherwise calm harbor, somehow under the thrall of the",
              "unique": false
            }
          ]
        },
        "2149": {
          "vnum": 2149,
          "name": "Submerged Passage",
          "description": "The water is cool though not unpleasantly so, and it is clear enough that you can see your surroundings quite clearly. Pools of darkness to the south and above your head indicate openings in those directions.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": 0,
