        "1576": {
          "vnum": 1576,
          "name": "The Reef",
          "description": "A brilliant menagerie of sea life makes its home here in the reef. Starfish cling to its surface like ornaments pasted there by a happy child. Most of the reef lays slightly beneath the surface and you pass over it without difficulty. A large, ocean-going vessel would certainly meet its doom here though; its underside smashed and torn by the sharp rock.",
