          "vnum": 2141,
          "name": "Wide Tunnel",
          "description": "The clammy air seems heavy in your lungs as you move along this wide rock tunnel. Wafts of fresh sea air swirl in from the north where a large cavern beckons. The tunnel narrows as it climbs further to the south.",
