          "vnum": 2150,
          "name": "The Reef",
          "description": "Some parts of the reef project above the surface of the water, but for the most part, the face of it lays just under the surface. It would definitely tear the bottom out of any ship unwary enough to run aground here. Fortunately, you don't sit too low in the water and can float right over.",
