          "name": "Top of the Shaft",
          "description": "You are standing on a ledge on the brink of a rough, circular shaft that drops into darkness. Hand and foot holds have been cut from the rock to make the climb easier. A mouldering, wooden panel is affixed to the north wall by rusted iron hinges.",
